                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-990-18470405 t18470405-990-punishment-109"></join>Judgment respired.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Sergeant.</hi>
